#: ../../H/hello-sailor-.rst:9
msgid ""
"Occasional West Coast equivalent of :ref:`hello-world`\\; seems to have "
"originated at SAIL, later associated with the game :ref:`Zork` (which also "
"included \"hello, aviator\" and \"hello, implementor\"). Originally from the"
" traditional hooker's greeting to a swabbie fresh off the boat, of course. "
"The standard response is \"Nothing happens here. \"; of all the Zork/Dungeon"
" games, only in Infocom's Zork 3 is \"Hello, Sailor\" actually useful "
"(excluding the unique situation where _knowing_ this fact is important in "
"Dungeon...)."
msgstr ""
"\\ :ref:`hello-world`\\ の時折見られる西海岸版。SAILで生まれたようで、後にゲーム\\ :ref:`Zork`\\ "
"(これには\"hello, aviator\"や\"hello, "
"implementor\"も含まれていた)と結びつけられた。もちろん元来は、船から降りたばかりの新米水兵への伝統的な娼婦の挨拶からである。標準的な応答は\"Nothing"
" happens here.\"(ここでは何も起こらない)である。Zork/Dungeonゲームのすべての中で、Infocomのzork "
"3でのみ\"Hello, Sailor\"が実際に役立つ(Dungeonにおいてこの事実を_知っていること_が重要になる特殊な状況を除いて...)。"
